# RQ-53-10-01-153: Lightning Strike Inspection

## Requirement Statement
After lightning strike event, nose cone shall undergo special inspection per AMM.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Visual inspection for burn marks, delamination
- Ultrasonic scan if damage visible
- Radar function test
- Bonding resistance check (< 2.5 milliohm)

## Compliance Status
Inspection procedure drafted
